Fluid grease unit : Refill with Shell Gadus S4 V45AC (Alternative: Shell Alvania 1029)
Hose lines and connections: Check leak tightness of connections;Check hoses for damage and wear (cracks)
Pressure settings: Check settings acc. to hydraulic plan
Filterelement : Check and replace if necessary
Hose line and connectings: Check leak tightness of connections;Check hoses for damage and wear (cracks)
Oil Level: Check oil level and quality of oil;Fill with Shell Tellus S2 MX 22 (Alternative: Mobil Velocite No. 10 ISO VG 22)
Uninterruptible power supply UPS: Check the power supply of the battery acc. to manufacturer specifications
Wiring: Visual inspection of the wiring especially in energy chains and drive connections
Every Emergency stop buttons: Checkfor damage and function
Toothed belt: Clean and replace if necessary
toothed bar drive: Clean, check for damage and replace if necessary toothed bar, toothed wheel, lubrication wheel
